** Ethernet Copper Cables. ( Copper Cables ).
	
		speed		name			ieee		called-are 	maximum-range
		10mpbs	ether			802.3i	10base-T		100m
		100mbps f-ether 	802.3u	100base-T 	100m
		1gbps		g-ether		802.3ab	1000base-T	100m
		10gbps  10g-ether 802.3an 10gbase-T		100m

** 3 Types Of Ethernet Cables.
	
		++ UTP CABLE. ( Unishield
		-- Unisheild Twister Pair Cables Nothing Provides To Inside Wires.

		++ STP CABLE. (Straight Throw Cable)
		-- Straight Throw Cables Inside Wires Covered With Shield. With Silver Cover.

		++ FIBER CABLE.
		-- Fiber Cables Are Used A Long Connection Network. Because Works With Laser Light
			 Technology.

		-- Needs To Connect SFP Connecter. ( Small Form Factor Plugable )


** 2 Types Of Copper Cables.

	 ++ Straight Throw Cable.
	 -- Straight Throw Cables Are Data Transmisson Pins Are.

			-----------------------
			1  transmit 1 receive
			2  transmit 2 receive
			3  receive  3 transmit
			6  receive  6 transmit
			------------------------

	 ++ Crossover Cable.
		
			----------------------
			1  transmit 3 receive
			2  transmit 6 receive
			3  receive  1 transmit
			6  receive  2 transmit
			-----------------------
		
